  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 168-piece LONDY Colorful Dreamer set combines rotating balls, standard support rods, and glow rods for colorful castle builds.",
      "The set includes 50 rotating balls, 70 standard support rods, 16 short glow rods, 14 long glow rods, clips, rings, storage bag, and flag.",
      "The pink color box is marked ages 5+ and includes a doodle activity area.",
      "Set total is RMB 187.67, shown as about $28.87."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "168件 LONDY Colorful Dreamer 结合旋转球、标准支撑杆和夜光杆，可搭建多彩城堡结构。",
      "套装包含50个旋转球、70根标准支撑杆、16根短夜光杆、14根长夜光杆、夹子、套圈、收纳袋和旗子。",
      "粉色彩盒标注适用 5 岁以上，并带有涂鸦互动区域。",
      "套装合计为人民币187.67元，折算约 $28.87。"
    ]
  },
